graph export "$data\trade_migration_scatter_2023.png", ///
    replace width(2000)
	
/*
 FIGURE INTERPRETATION:

 The 2023 cross-sectional scatterplot displays a moderately negative fitted relationship between extra-EU trade openness and net migration.

 However, there is substantial dispersion across countries. Malta is
